Staggering collection of subliminal messages..

Just wanted to tell everyone that this particular rip wouldn't play on my stand-alone DivX player.

I had to AVIrecode/resize the avi to 720X540 to get it to play on TV.

Just to tell you that it probably will play better on your PC. Res. is 800X600. Framerate is 32.
